986
01:03:33.684 --> 01:03:36.813
I told each of them I'd let them off
if they gave me one name.

987
01:03:36.896 --> 01:03:37.980
and they all told me.

988
01:03:38.064 --> 01:03:38.898
Nice.

989
01:03:53.621 --> 01:03:56.916
All I did was buy him one cup of tea
during the consultation.

990
01:03:56.999 --> 01:03:59.585
We will speak when my attorney gets here!

991
01:03:59.669 --> 01:04:01.838
So what? I'm an assemblyman.
Don't touch me!

992
01:04:01.921 --> 01:04:03.297
Attorney Kang. where are you?

993
01:04:03.381 --> 01:04:05.716
-Why the hell aren't you here already?
-Please sit.

994
01:04:25.695 --> 01:04:29.198
I want to show you
how you ruined a child's life.

995
01:06:31.737 --> 01:06:34.699
Subtitle translation by: Lisa Kim

